{"tid":597606,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人覺得中學時期係自己最輝煌既時刻？","createTime":"2018-03-18T19:34:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-19T01:05:25.000Z","uid":143363,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"2a0845c71f4278975a225075afd4af2427f9e861","tid":597606,"uid":143363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T19:34:28.000Z","msg":"中學果時競爭力低，自己讀書唔差，全部都有頭十。<br />\n陸運會又有牌拎下，又有打下社籃咁。<br />\n自然識唔少女同學。<br />\n最記得中六果年DSE ，成日教個女仔ICT，都叫做曖味緊。<br />\n點知佢考完個試就去左外國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，而我只係留係香港讀大學既傻仔。<br />\n仲記得佢走之前成日WhatsApp ，直至去左外國一排就無疾而終<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上到大學啲人勁左好多，愈來愈冇自信，開始覺得自己原來都係一個中下之人，唔特別聰明，講野唔叻，只係有少少勤力，反而個人深沈左，少說話多做事，或者就係你地口中所講既毒撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上年出黎做野更加唔洗講啦，日日做做做，迷失左。<br />\n有時就會想當年，好似今晚咁，掛住個女仔。但聽日呢，又變番行屍走肉。<br />\n唉，唔講咁多，聽日仲要準時返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4e12cc774b2a0f4850fa3a0d2cd8c89b11d4aef","tid":597606,"uid":43231,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T19:39:28.000Z","msg":"我最靚仔多fd都算係中學時期<br />\n之後越來越越毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fab97e506b433b40e4831762f3194ccfd16b495f","tid":597606,"uid":41943,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T19:55:05.000Z","msg":"真。。。D1學界。。。<br />\nCheering....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3c3cebcfcb30ce09493fccaba58ec1e24796516","tid":597606,"uid":174084,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T00:58:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.am730.com.hk/column/%E8%B2%A1%E7%B6%93/%E7%A9%B6%E7%AB%9F%E7%94%9A%E9%BA%BC%E6%98%AF%E5%8F%BB%EF%BC%9F-27371\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.am730.com.hk%2Fcolumn%2F%25E8%25B2%25A1%25E7%25B6%2593%2F%25E7%25A9%25B6%25E7%25AB%259F%25E7%2594%259A%25E9%25BA%25BC%25E6%2598%25AF%25E5%258F%25BB%25EF%25BC%259F-27371&d=i42euQ6IMgmSN7yCN6aTHaEKYqckrLkk14koP0tj2xA%3D&h=da3b95aa\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.am730.com.hk/column/%E8%B2%A1%E7%B6%93/%E7%A9%B6%E7%AB%9F%E7%94%9A%E9%BA%BC%E6%98%AF%E5%8F%BB%EF%BC%9F-27371</a><br />\n<br />\n別說是會考拿A了，就算是大學拿到一級榮譽，甚至在名牌大學拿到博士學位，也沒有甚麼了不起的地方，因為這些只是一個起點，要想真正在讀書做學問的方面有成就，必須能夠著書立說，成一家之言，才能夠受到人的敬重，才能夠算是叻，才能夠算是成功。<br />\n<br />\n如果一個成年人，年紀不輕，還去到處炫耀自己在那間中學、那間大學就讀，甚至是自己的智商有多高，那麼，這個人的成就一定有限得很。"},{"pid":"e3f79e1bf28bbcb48bb9321e66cc4307693fb7ba","tid":597606,"uid":121249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T01:02:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9f601db3ecb2580e4ada507199846608d89d375","tid":597606,"uid":49853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T01:05:25.000Z","msg":"由細到大都冇風光過<br />\n長期係下游位置<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}